@{
    ViewBag.Title = "FAQ";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}
<style>
.card {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    transition: 0.3s;
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 5px;
    background-color: white;
    height:70px;
    /*color: white;*/
}

.card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 8px 16px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
}

img {
    border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
}

.container {
    padding: 2px 16px;
}
/*<!--color for odd nd even rows-->*/



/*<!--end of color for odd nd even rows-->*/

</style>
<div class="widget widget-padding ">
    <div class="widget-header">
        <i class="fa fa-star-half-o" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <h5>FAQ</h5>
    </div>

    <div class="row-fluid" style="margin-bottom: 12px; margin-top: 5px;">
        <div class="widget-body" style="border: 0">
            <div class="row-fluid">
                <div class="widget span12">
                    <div class="widget-body clearfix" style="overflow-x: auto">
                        <div id="ReportTotal">
                            <div class="box">
                                <div class="box-content padded" style="background: white;">
                                    <form class="row-fluid">
                                        <div class="col-md-12">
                                            <div class="col-md-12 padded">
                                                <div class="card padded">
                                                    <b>Q1. I can't see my custom report!</b>
                                                    <br />
                                                    <p>Ans. All customized reports navigation has been moved to Customized Report. Please visit Customized Report to see the custom reports. </p>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                             <div class="col-md-12 padded">
                                                <div class="card padded">
                                                    <b>Q2. Custom reports are still not in Customized Report!</b>
                                                    <br />
                                                    <p>Ans.Please email to <a href="mailto: customerservice@blackboxgps.net" target="_top"> customerservice@blackboxgps.net</a> with your loginId and report Name.</p>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                             <div class="col-md-12 padded">
                                               <div class="card padded">
                                                    <b>Q3.What is fleet management system?</b>
                                                    <br />
                                                    <p>Ans. FMS is a standard interface to gather, store, process, monitor, report export information of commercial vehicles.</p>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                             <div class="col-md-12 padded">
                                                 <div class="card padded">
                                                    <b>Q4.How to recharge my SMS pack?</b>
                                                    <br />
                                                    <p>Ans. Through Online payment. Go to <a href="@Url.Action("AddSmsForCustomer","smsportal")"> My Account-> Buy SMS.</a> Select the desired SMS package and follow the payment instructions. </p>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                             <div class="col-md-12 padded">
                                                 <div class="card padded">
                                                    <b>Q5.What are add-on reports?</b>
                                                    <br />
                                                    <p>Ans.Add-on reports are the reports apart from standard GPS reports that may require additional hardware at an additional cost.</p>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="col-md-12 padded">
                                                 <div class="card padded">
                                                    <b>Q6.What is six-eye map?</b>
                                                    <br />
                                                    <p>Ans.It is an extension to previous four-eye map. Showing all the 6 different status that a vehicle can be in.</p>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="col-md-12 padded">
                                                 <div class="card padded">
                                                    <b>Q7.Where are the vehicle documents alerts?</b>
                                                    <br />
                                                    <p>Ans. Many alerts including vehicle & driver docs are now part of fms. Navigate to FMS->Renewal reminder to view and add vehilce documents alerts.     </p>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                              <div class="col-md-12 padded">
                                                 <div class="card padded">
                                                    <b>Q8.What is trip report?</b>
                                                    <br />
                                                    <p>Ans. Trip report helps to calculate ETA of vehicles following a particular trip. Trip needs to be added & assigned to vehciles.</p>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                              <div class="col-md-12 padded">
                                                 <div class="card padded">
                                                    <b>Q9.In Route Playback, Route with Direction and Route with Stoppage is missing?</b>
                                                    <br />
                                                    <p>Ans. All have been merged in single window for better user experience. Use the toggle buttons to view stoppages, POIs and Geofence while viewing the Route Playback.</p>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </form>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
